006package gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.model;
007
008import edu.umd.cs.findbugs.annotations.NonNull;
009
010/**
011 * A base class for an assembly definition defined globally within a Metaschema
012 * module.
013 *
014 * @param <MODULE>
015 *          the Java type of the containing module
016 * @param <INSTANCE>
017 *          the expected Java type of an instance of this definition
018 * @param <FLAG>
019 *          the expected Java type of flag children
020 * @param <MODEL>
021 *          the expected Java type of model children
022 * @param <NAMED_MODEL>
023 *          the expected Java type of named model children
024 * @param <FIELD>
025 *          the expected Java type of field children
026 * @param <ASSEMBLY>
027 *          the expected Java type of assembly children
028 * @param <CHOICE>
029 *          the expected Java type of choice children
030 * @param <CHOICE_GROUP>
031 *          the expected Java type of choice group children
032 */
033public abstract class AbstractGlobalAssemblyDefinition<
034    MODULE extends IModule,
035    INSTANCE extends IAssemblyInstance,
036    FLAG extends IFlagInstance,
037    MODEL extends IModelInstanceAbsolute,
038    NAMED_MODEL extends INamedModelInstanceAbsolute,
039    FIELD extends IFieldInstanceAbsolute,
040    ASSEMBLY extends IAssemblyInstanceAbsolute,
041    CHOICE extends IChoiceInstance,
042    CHOICE_GROUP extends IChoiceGroupInstance>
043    extends AbstractGlobalDefinition<MODULE, INSTANCE>
044    implements IAssemblyDefinition, IFeatureContainerFlag<FLAG>, IFeatureContainerModelAssembly<
045        MODEL,
046        NAMED_MODEL,
047        FIELD,
048        ASSEMBLY,
049        CHOICE,
050        CHOICE_GROUP> {
051
052  /**
053   * Construct a new global assembly definition.
054   *
055   * @param module
056   *          the parent module containing this definition
057   */
058  protected AbstractGlobalAssemblyDefinition(@NonNull MODULE module) {
059    super(module, module::toModelQName);
060  }
061}
